prepare_country_data <- function(country_code, P) {  modelM <- P$modelM  modelQ <- P$modelQ    # ---- SET DYNAMIC PATHS ----  DataFile <- paste0("Data/", country_code, "/Processed/Data_", country_code, ".xlsx")  LegendFile <- paste0("Data/", country_code, "/Original/Legend_", country_code, ".xlsx")    # ---- LOAD MONTHLY DATA ----  monthly_data <- readxl::read_excel(DataFile, sheet = "MonthlyLong", col_names = TRUE)  DataM <- monthly_data[, -1]  DatesM <- as.Date(monthly_data[[1]])    legend_m <- readxl::read_excel(LegendFile, sheet = "MDescriptionFull")  model_col_m <- which(colnames(legend_m) == modelM)  ListM <- which((legend_m[, model_col_m]) == 1)    DataM <- DataM[, ListM]  GroupM <- legend_m[ListM, 16]  SeriesM <- legend_m[ListM, 1]  TransfM <- floor(legend_m[ListM, 8])  UnbM <- legend_m[ListM, 12:14]  ClassM <- legend_m[ListM, 11]    DataMTrf <- DataM  annualize_idx <- which(TransfM[[1]] %in% c(2, 4))  DataMTrf[, annualize_idx] <- DataMTrf[, annualize_idx] * 100    CovidNaN <- function(data, dates, class, start_covid, end_covid) {    real_idx <- which(grepl("r", tolower(class)))    mask <- dates >= as.Date(as.yearmon(start_covid)) & dates <= as.Date(as.yearmon(end_covid))    covid_matrix <- matrix(FALSE, nrow = nrow(data), ncol = ncol(data))    covid_matrix[mask, real_idx] <- TRUE    data[covid_matrix] <- NA    list(data, covid_matrix)  }    resM <- CovidNaN(DataMTrf, DatesM, ClassM[[1]], P$covid_start, P$covid_end)  DataMTrf <- resM[[1]]  Covid_obsM <- resM[[2]]  T_M <- nrow(DataMTrf)    # ---- LOAD QUARTERLY DATA ----  quarterly_data <- readxl::read_excel(DataFile, sheet = "QuarterlyLong", col_names = TRUE)  DataQ <- quarterly_data[, -1]  DatesQ <- as.Date(quarterly_data[[1]])    legend_q <- readxl::read_excel(LegendFile, sheet = "QDescriptionFull")  model_col_q <- which(colnames(legend_q) == modelQ)  ListQ <- which((legend_q[, model_col_q]) == 1)    DataQ <- DataQ[, ListQ]  GroupQ <- legend_q[ListQ, 16]  SeriesQ <- legend_q[ListQ, 1]  TransfQ <- floor(legend_q[ListQ, 8])  UnbQ <- legend_q[ListQ, 12:14]  ClassQ <- legend_q[ListQ, 11]    DataQTrf <- DataQ  annualize_q <- which(TransfQ[[1]] %in% c(2, 4))  DataQTrf[, annualize_q] <- DataQTrf[, annualize_q] * 100    resQ <- CovidNaN(DataQTrf, DatesQ, ClassQ[[1]], P$covid_start, P$covid_end)  DataQTrf <- resQ[[1]]  Covid_obsQ <- resQ[[2]]    DataQMTrf <- do.call(rbind, lapply(1:nrow(DataQTrf), function(i) {    rbind(rep(NA, ncol(DataQTrf)),          rep(NA, ncol(DataQTrf)),          DataQTrf[i, ])  }))  T_Q <- nrow(DataQMTrf)    T_final <- max(T_M, T_Q)  if (T_M < T_final) {    paddingM <- data.frame(matrix(NA, T_final - T_M, ncol(DataMTrf)))    colnames(paddingM) <- colnames(DataMTrf)    DataMTrf <- rbind(DataMTrf, paddingM)  }  if (T_Q < T_final) {    paddingQ <- data.frame(matrix(NA, T_final - T_Q, ncol(DataQMTrf)))    colnames(paddingQ) <- colnames(DataQMTrf)    DataQMTrf <- rbind(DataQMTrf, paddingQ)  }    Data <- cbind(DataMTrf, DataQMTrf)  Series <- c(SeriesM, SeriesQ)  Group <- c(GroupM, GroupQ)  UnbPatt <- rbind(UnbM, UnbQ)    result <- list(    Data = Data,    DatesM = DatesM,    DatesQ = DatesQ,    Series = Series,    Group = Group,    UnbalancedPattern = UnbPatt,    Covid_obsM = Covid_obsM,    Covid_obsQ = Covid_obsQ,    Name = paste0("Data_", country_code)  )    assign(result$Name, result$Data, envir = .GlobalEnv)  result$quarterly_start_idx <- ncol(DataMTrf) + 1  return(result)}# Select the variable by GDP correlationprepare_country_data_auto <- function(country_code, P) {  modelM <- P$modelM  modelQ <- P$modelQ    # === LOAD PATHS ===  DataFile <- paste0("Data/", country_code, "/Processed/Data_", country_code, ".xlsx")  LegendFile <- paste0("Data/", country_code, "/Original/Legend_", country_code, ".xlsx")    # === LOAD DATA ===  monthly_data <- readxl::read_excel(DataFile, sheet = "MonthlyLong")  quarterly_data <- readxl::read_excel(DataFile, sheet = "QuarterlyLong")  legend_m <- readxl::read_excel(LegendFile, sheet = "MDescriptionFull")  legend_q <- readxl::read_excel(LegendFile, sheet = "QDescriptionFull")    DatesM <- as.Date(monthly_data[[1]])  DatesQ <- as.Date(quarterly_data[[1]])  DataM <- monthly_data[, -1]  DataQ <- quarterly_data[, -1]    # === Identify GDP columns ===  gdp_q_idx <- which(grepl("^GDP_", colnames(DataQ), ignore.case = TRUE))[1]  gdp_q_series <- DataQ[[gdp_q_idx]]    # === Select variables by correlation with GDP ===  select_top_corr <- function(data, gdp, n) {    cors <- apply(data, 2, function(x) suppressWarnings(cor(x, gdp, use = "pairwise.complete.obs")))    top_idx <- order(abs(cors), decreasing = TRUE)[1:min(n, length(cors))]    return(top_idx)  }    # === Determine size based on model type ===  model_sizes <- list(    small = list(Q = 1, M = 10),    medium = list(Q = 5, M = 20),    large = list(Q = 10, M = 30)  )    n_q <- model_sizes[[tolower(modelQ)]]$Q  n_m <- model_sizes[[tolower(modelM)]]$M    # === Select top series ===  topM <- select_top_corr(DataM, rep(gdp_q_series, each = 3)[1:nrow(DataM)], n_m)  topQ <- select_top_corr(DataQ, gdp_q_series, n_q)    DataMTrf <- DataM[, topM]  DataQTrf <- DataQ[, topQ]  SeriesM <- colnames(DataMTrf)  SeriesQ <- colnames(DataQTrf)    # === Annualize transformations ===  transf_m <- floor(legend_m[match(SeriesM, legend_m[[1]]), 8])  transf_q <- floor(legend_q[match(SeriesQ, legend_q[[1]]), 8])  DataMTrf[, transf_m %in% c(2, 4)] <- DataMTrf[, transf_m %in% c(2, 4)] * 100  DataQTrf[, transf_q %in% c(2, 4)] <- DataQTrf[, transf_q %in% c(2, 4)] * 100    # === Apply COVID NA pattern ===  CovidNaN <- function(data, dates, class, start_covid, end_covid) {    real_idx <- which(grepl("r", tolower(class)))    mask <- dates >= as.Date(as.yearmon(start_covid)) & dates <= as.Date(as.yearmon(end_covid))    covid_matrix <- matrix(FALSE, nrow = nrow(data), ncol = ncol(data))    covid_matrix[mask, real_idx] <- TRUE    data[covid_matrix] <- NA    list(data, covid_matrix)  }    ClassM <- legend_m[match(SeriesM, legend_m[[1]]), 11][[1]]  ClassQ <- legend_q[match(SeriesQ, legend_q[[1]]), 11][[1]]  resM <- CovidNaN(DataMTrf, DatesM, ClassM, P$covid_start, P$covid_end)  resQ <- CovidNaN(DataQTrf, DatesQ, ClassQ, P$covid_start, P$covid_end)  DataMTrf <- resM[[1]]  Covid_obsM <- resM[[2]]  DataQTrf <- resQ[[1]]  Covid_obsQ <- resQ[[2]]    # === Expand Quarterly data to Monthly ===  DataQMTrf <- do.call(rbind, lapply(1:nrow(DataQTrf), function(i) {    rbind(rep(NA, ncol(DataQTrf)),          rep(NA, ncol(DataQTrf)),          DataQTrf[i, ])  }))    # === Pad to same number of rows ===  T_final <- max(nrow(DataMTrf), nrow(DataQMTrf))  # Padding mensile  if (nrow(DataMTrf) < T_final) {    paddingM <- matrix(NA, nrow = T_final - nrow(DataMTrf), ncol = ncol(DataMTrf))    colnames(paddingM) <- colnames(DataMTrf)  # preserva i nomi    DataMTrf <- rbind(DataMTrf, paddingM)  }    # Padding trimestrale  if (nrow(DataQMTrf) < T_final) {    paddingQ <- matrix(NA, nrow = T_final - nrow(DataQMTrf), ncol = ncol(DataQMTrf))    colnames(paddingQ) <- colnames(DataQMTrf)  # preserva i nomi    DataQMTrf <- rbind(DataQMTrf, paddingQ)  }      # === Final output ===  Data <- cbind(DataMTrf, DataQMTrf)  Series <- c(SeriesM, SeriesQ)    result <- list(    Data = Data,    Dates = DatesM,    Series = Series,    quarterly_start_idx = ncol(DataMTrf) + 1,    Covid_obsM = Covid_obsM,    Covid_obsQ = Covid_obsQ  )    assign(paste0("Data_", country_code), result$Data, envir = .GlobalEnv)  return(result)}PK    qYrYy`6  ӻ   y/ykCJЮ+x2XQ]Q}C46q<6I4,@%%ǳ6xP	iX>_ȓh)-*(2Ì4>JnqбP㮪pxl =P㥓4Ϙ]UcL-'kk4qS"J|{ u낺1Su܍ ~#8= l؂6o[~Q Ѳ!<ud&J^j!~{B.%zUJ`R!\Yu(qEtY&ŁECkkev:VXhQE}<^.=~AX<4d_h_n_`0 y>9s[B,z\F͙s圫l&m1sσ@)d.⼋w*Xe6k:[vi&[sΈ?6!I3+{IM/,~}gg&MӔ]eL	fP,B6n=+q#'e?z_|:dUkg :?bv-us폾"WiG7ߙa`j{z`P.&"I>&B߻o1ىReH48	ާLy(	_ꏯKMCqMKNS28 k	gLQ384[ZTNK9iˉ*Lqp)gE{dq4B6VJq$ȀAE^v)OW~ȋִq#	:2Ydi~w3	"d2#L`		2pr	$cLr*H&HRv"9-P1,fc"1,fcxD}1ŕB2Q"cuh8(bt cYT^VekO Uõ`Z-&&iiD*pA).ݰbCv|>
